service: amz-backend  # Corrected service name

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: us-east-1

functions:
  uploadImage:
    handler: handler.uploadImage
    events:
      - http:
          path: upload
          method: post

  getImages:
    handler: handler.getImages
    events:
      - http:
          path: images
          method: get

resources:
  Resources:
    ImagesBucket:
      Type: AWS::S3::Bucket
      Properties:
        BucketName: our-images-amz
